    <title>SSSHR 資料更新到 Progress 流程</title>
    <url>/2021/08/12/data-adf2progress/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="SSHR-資料更新到-Progress-流程"><a href="#SSHR-資料更新到-Progress-流程" class="headerlink" title="SSHR 資料更新到 Progress 流程"></a>SSHR 資料更新到 Progress 流程</h1><h2 id="Data-Flow-oracle-gt-oracle-gt-progress"><a href="#Data-Flow-oracle-gt-oracle-gt-progress" class="headerlink" title="Data Flow (oracle&gt;oracle&gt;progress)"></a>Data Flow (oracle&gt;oracle&gt;progress)</h2><table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>FLOW</th>
<th>oracle &gt;&gt;</th>
<th>oracle &gt;&gt;</th>
<th>progress</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody><tr>
<td>DB</td>
<td>hrlink@ADF_HRDB</td>
<td>progress@ETL_COGNOSCM</td>
<td>BISYS@twhr</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Table</td>
<td>EMPLOYEE0_NATIONAL_INSUR_LOG</td>
<td>ADF_EMPLOYEE0_TEMP</td>
<td>PUB.EMPLOYEE0</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
<span id="more"></span>
<h2 id="SSIS-畫面"><a href="#SSIS-畫面" class="headerlink" title="SSIS 畫面"></a>SSIS 畫面</h2><p><img src="/images/data_adf2prokgress/adf2pprgress-1.png" alt="justNote-init-1"></p>
<h2 id="oracle-gt-gt-oracle"><a href="#oracle-gt-gt-oracle" class="headerlink" title="oracle &gt;&gt; oracle"></a>oracle &gt;&gt; oracle</h2><h3 id="執行procedure"><a href="#執行procedure" class="headerlink" title="執行procedure :"></a>執行procedure :</h3><pre><code>progress@ETL_COGNOSCM 執行procedure : P_ADF_EMP0_TO_PGS
</code></pre>
<h3 id="暫存的Table"><a href="#暫存的Table" class="headerlink" title="暫存的Table"></a>暫存的Table</h3> <figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> <span class="operator">*</span> <span class="keyword">from</span> ADF_EMPLOYEE0_TEMP t </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="篩選要匯入的資料列-close-flag-2-HR核可"><a href="#篩選要匯入的資料列-close-flag-2-HR核可" class="headerlink" title="篩選要匯入的資料列(close_flag = 2 HR核可):"></a>篩選要匯入的資料列(close_flag = 2 HR核可):</h3> <figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> <span class="number">1</span> data_ori, doc_id</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">from</span> employee0_basic_log<span class="variable">@adf</span>_hr</span><br><span class="line">     <span class="keyword">where</span> close_flag <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">2</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">union</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">select</span> <span class="number">2</span> data_ori, doc_id</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">from</span> employee0_education_log<span class="variable">@adf</span>_hr</span><br><span class="line">     <span class="keyword">where</span> close_flag <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">2</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">union</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">select</span> <span class="number">3</span> data_ori, doc_id</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">from</span> employee0_group_insur_log<span class="variable">@adf</span>_hr</span><br><span class="line">     <span class="keyword">where</span> close_flag <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">2</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">union</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">select</span> <span class="number">4</span> data_ori, doc_id</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">from</span> employee0_licence_log<span class="variable">@adf</span>_hr</span><br><span class="line">     <span class="keyword">where</span> close_flag <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">2</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">union</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">select</span> <span class="number">5</span> data_ori, doc_id</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">from</span> employee0_national_insur_log<span class="variable">@adf</span>_hr</span><br><span class="line">     <span class="keyword">where</span> close_flag <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">2</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">UNION</span> </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">SELECT</span> <span class="number">6</span> data_ori, doc_id</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">FROM</span> employee0_retire_log<span class="variable">@adf</span>_hr</span><br><span class="line">       <span class="keyword">WHERE</span> close_flag <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">2</span></span><br><span class="line">     <span class="keyword">order</span> <span class="keyword">by</span> doc_id;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="oracle-gt-gt-progress"><a href="#oracle-gt-gt-progress" class="headerlink" title="oracle &gt;&gt; progress"></a>oracle &gt;&gt; progress</h2><p><img src="/images/data_adf2prokgress/adf2pprgress-2.png" alt="justNote-init-2"></p>
<h2 id="排程執行"><a href="#排程執行" class="headerlink" title="排程執行"></a>排程執行</h2><p><img src="/images/data_adf2prokgress/adf2pprgress-3.png" alt="justNote-init-3"></p>
<h2 id="Progress-內部更新流程"><a href="#Progress-內部更新流程" class="headerlink" title="Progress 內部更新流程"></a>Progress 內部更新流程</h2><pre><code>資料匯入pub.employee0 TX_FLAG=2,隨即被複製到正式TABLE 然後刪掉該筆
所以一般只會看到TX_FLAG=&quot;Y&quot;或&quot;N&quot; 的那一筆
如果有TX_FLAG= &quot;N&quot; 的資料，每天中午會匯到SSHR然後將 TX_FLAG= &quot;Y&quot;
</code></pre>
<p><img src="/images/data_adf2prokgress/adf2pprgress-4.png" alt="justNote-init-4"></p>
]]></content>
